data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_0671a3e91f2c70da006a0aef1774e48193925cbc80e8262347","logprobs":[],"output_index":0,"sequence_number":134,"text":"One innovative solution for reducing food waste in restaurants is the implementation of a \"Smart Waste Tracking System.\"\n\n**Idea:** The Smart Waste Tracking System involves using IoT-enabled sensors in waste bins to monitor the types and amounts of food being discarded. This system could provide real-time data analytics to help restaurants identify waste patterns, adjust portion sizes, menu offerings, and optimize inventory.\n\n**Category:** Technology\n\n**Feasibility:** 7\n\n**Resources:** \n- IoT sensors and hardware for waste bins\n- Software platform for data analysis\n- Historical data on food usage and waste\n- Staff training for system usage\n- Initial investment for technology setup"}

